graph TD
    A[End of Training Job] -->|Saves state_dict| B[model.pth]
    C[model.py Architecture Class] --> D[Package into Archive]
    B --> D
    
    D -->|Uploads via SDK| E[S3: model.tar.gz]
    
    subgraph SageMaker Endpoint Initialization
    E -->|Downloads to container| F[model_fn]
    F -->|Instantiates Architecture & Loads Weights| G[Model Loaded in RAM]
    end
    
    subgraph Real-Time Inference
    H[React Web App JSON Payload] -->|HTTP POST| I[input_fn]
    I -->|Returns PyTorch Tensor| J[predict_fn]
    J -->|Calls model.forward| G
    G -->|Raw Output| J
    J --> K[output_fn]
    K -->|Returns JSON| L[React Web App Response]
    end
